<p><placeName>Colorado </placeName><date when="1822-10-16">October 16th 1822</date></p>
<p><persName>Mr  Stephen F. Austin</persName>    Sir please pay <persName>Mr  Robert Cuykendall</persName>
Thirty dollars and it shall be an offset for so much in our 
<placeName>Settlement</placeName></p>

<p>Yours etc</p>

<p><persName>Robert C. Bruffey</persName></p>

<p>[Endorsed:] Recd the within of <persName>S. F. Austin</persName> <date when="1828-12-06">Decb. 6, 1828</date> <persName>Robert
Kuykendell</persName></p>

        </div1>
